##The 21-year-old doctor who died in the collapse envied his friend on the front line

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Reporter for the paper, Wang Xuanhui, intern, Zheng Xu, Xu Yiying

Shortly after 8:00 pm on March 7, Tang Shuangping was driving, and a news flash popped up from his mobile phone: "Many people were buried in the collapse of the Xinjia hotel in Quanzhou, Fujian Province. ".

"This is not the son on Duty Hotel? " Tang shuangping emergency stop car, immediately dial the son Tang Fan's telephone, "sorry you dial the telephone temporarily unable to connect... "

Too late to think more, Tang shuangping straight drive to Xinjia hotel. However, the scene can only see a piece of debris, firefighters and medical personnel are gradually reinforcement.

A few days crouching, anxious Tang Shuangping did not wait to want the news. On the afternoon of March 10, Tang Fan was confirmed dead by his family. The grief of losing a son in Middle Age, let Tang Shuangping direct coma pass by.

Dr. Tang Fan. This article is provided by the interviewee

Tang Fan, 21, is a young doctor in the Medical Imaging Department of Wanxiang Hospital in Quanzhou. He has been working there for less than a year. Last July, he returned to Quanzhou after a year of volunteering to aid Xinjiang.

In mid-february, Xinjia hotel was designated as a central medical observation point for people from Lei Cheng district, a key area of NCP outside Fujian Province. Tang was then assigned to the hotel to take charge of routine epidemic prevention work and was on duty on the night of the building collapse.

In the life, Tang Fan is the sunshine youth in the eye of friend, can sing, like to play guitar, occasionally also play"eat chicken game". Among friends, Tang shares his thoughts.

Wang Sinan, a doctor in a health center in Lianjiang County, Fuzhou City, is Tang Fan's childhood friend. Shortly after the outbreak, he went to work in the quarantine zone. "Tang Fan told me that he envied me for working on the front line of the epidemic. Today, however, he fell on the front line. "

Tang Fan and Wang Sinan talked a lot, including career, parents, love. Together, they made a pact that their success would outpace their parents'aging.

No one could have predicted that night, the hotel collapsed and took away his young life.

Medical School

Tang Shuangping, a native of Dongkou County in Hunan Province, came to Quanzhou in the 1990s. Quanzhou, on the east coast of Fujian Province, is one of the most developed areas of the private economy and is the first choice for many people to work and start their own businesses.

When he was three, he followed his parents to Quanzhou, where he has remained ever since. After a series of struggles, they finally settled down in Quanzhou. Tang's father works for an insurance company, his mother runs a barbecue stand for the night market and has a 15-year-old sister.

"after graduating from junior high school, he told me he wanted to be a doctor, and I agreed, " Tang said. Tang later enrolled in the Quanzhou Medical Vocational School and became a five-year junior college student majoring in medical imaging technology.

As luck would have it, Wang Sinan, a good friend from his primary school class, also applied for the major and was in the same class. They were also assigned to the same dorm.

Why did you choose medicine? Tang Fan has not talked to Wang Sinan directly about this topic. In Wang Sinan's view, Tang Fan is a "doctor of the heart" of the people, warm-hearted, kind-hearted, positive.

"In my eyes, Tang fan is a person who works actively and has integrity, " Wang Sinan said in an interview with the paper. In the school, Tang Fan because personality lively, so very popular, often participate in voluntary activities. In College, the two of them volunteered together at book rafting events.

In College, Tang learned to play the guitar out of interest, sometimes practicing in his dorm room and performing once upon graduation. He also enjoys physical exercise and often goes for a run with Wang Sinan.

For the actor, Tang Fan Likes Hu Ge a little more, belongs to "likes but does not follow the Star" the type. Wang Sinan said that when attending school Tang Fan's living expenses are not many, in order to save often goes home, is in the university dormitory most often goes home one.

"although his face is young, his mind is mature. His inner conviction is already strong and strong, and he understands responsibility and thinking for his parents. " According to Liu Yangcheng, a college counselor, Tang Fan is a very responsible student.

Every September when the school year starts, he will take the initiative to help teachers undertake some things, to help teachers prepare for the new students. Tang, who is part of the school's Volunteer Association, tries his best to help his classmates. "sometimes there are more things to do, and I ask him to help me do some things, " Liu said.

In the school, Liu Yangcheng often carries out medical ethics education to the schoolmates. "actually, doctors don't necessarily have so many brilliant ideals, but they do know what responsibility is. " Tang fan is a good student and a responsible doctor, he said, they practiced the training of medical imaging technique class ——"medical treatment for benevolence, knowledge for virtue" .

Aid Xinjiang

After graduating from university in July 2018, Tang chose to join Xinjiang instead of working directly. After the recommendation of the school, strict examination, he became a college student Volunteer Service Program in western Xinjiang special activities of a volunteer.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
During the volunteer service, the partners celebrate the birthday of Tang Fan.

"I told him it's good for boys to go to Xinjiang to exercise, " said his father, Tang Shuangping, when discussing his decision to volunteer for Xinjiang

Before setting out for Xinjiang, Wang Sinan came to see him off, invited him to have a meal, told him to take care of himself and pay attention to his safety during his stay in Xinjiang. "When we arrive in Xinjiang, we will often contact everyone and tell them that he is living well there. Please rest assured. "

Tang, who serves in Mori Kazakh Autonomous County under the Changji Hui Autonomous Prefecture, a Fujian counterpart, was assigned to the County Commission for Discipline Inspection and supervision.

Wang Ruihong, a volunteer colleague at the aid group in Mori Kazakh Autonomous County, recalled to thepaper.cn that there were 11 volunteers in the same year as Tang, five of whom were from outside the province. "Tang Fan is the handsomest of the volunteers. In winter, he always says 'be cool, not warm' . Everyone reminds him to wear more clothes. "

In Mori Kazakh Autonomous County, perhaps because of the water and soil diet, Tang Fan's stomach is always uncomfortable. Wang Ruihong often takes him to the hospital by taxi. But Tang fan is very polite, and always around the people said: "I'm fine. "

Learning of Tang's death, Shelley, a member of the Standing Committee of the Mori Kazakh Autonomous County Commission for Discipline Inspection, spoke to the paper about her memories of him.

At first, colleagues in the units he supported said, "really? ! " "Wait for the final search and rescue information? ! " Shelley said. No one was willing to accept that.

Tang fan is Shelley's youngest colleague in more than 20 years. She remembers that in early August 2018, when Tang Fan had just been assigned to her unit by the Youth League Committee of the Autonomous Region and the County Youth League committee, she went to a meeting to pick him up, "He was a young man with a boyish face, fair skin and a shy face when he first met New People. "

When Shelley learned that Tang was the only boy in the family, he asked him, "then how did your parents let you come so far to Xinjiang? " Tang said, "I am a boy, so I should go to the hard and remote places for training. "

Shelley was surprised by his response, thinking: a child of the 1990s can have such ideas and practices, can give him a big "like. ". During the year of Voluntary Service, Tang Fan worked in the Department of Organization, Office, Party Work Room, anti-crime office and other departments. "Although Tang was a medical student, he was computer-literate, stable and introverted, and he was able to get along happily with his colleagues from all ethnic groups in the offices and towns of Mori Kazakh Autonomous County, " Shelley recalls.

"He spoke with a strong southern accent and didn't say much, " Shelley said, adding that he had arranged for Tang to sit in the same office as his 50-year-old Kazakhs brother, who was well-versed in his work, hope that first, he will not feel lonely in a foreign country, second, you can calm down to follow the study and exercise.

Shelley said that over the past year, Tang Fan to help organize cadre files, to participate in the unit on duty, holidays and colleagues also in-depth township, village inspection, to participate in the verification of office buildings. In his spare time, he studies in the office with books on medicine.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
When he arrived in Xinjiang, Tang fan quickly blended in. He sang with colleagues at the 2019 youth mixer.

Soon, Tang Fan was blending in. At the local 2019 Youth Soiree, Tang also performed and performed a duet of two songs, "write a poem for you" and "Fairy Tales" , with colleagues.

Tang Fan in Xinjiang has always been worried about his parents and younger sister, Liu said. On June 14,2019, Tang Fan posted a message on a friend's circle: "Xinjiang is more beautiful than Liangjing, Fujian is more beautiful than missing. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
During the process of aiding Xinjiang, he still had his heart set on Fujian.

During the period of voluntary service, Tang Fan participated in the civil service, public institutions entrance examination. In July 2019, after a year of service, Tang returned to Quanzhou.

After returning from Xinjiang, Tang Fan also went back to school to communicate with Liu Yangcheng. "This year has given him a great change. He knows where his home is and where his roots are. "

Dead

When Tang returned to Quanzhou, he encouraged him to work first and then prepare for the public hospital or civil service exam, Liu said. Soon, Tang Fan in Quanzhou Wanxiang hospital successful application, become the hospital's imaging department of a doctor.

Back in Fujian, Tang Fan and Wang Sinan have more contact. They talked a lot, including career, parents, love. Tang fan also shares some thoughts on relationships with friends.

"Life is unfair and happiness always comes at a price, but even so, so many people enjoy it and hope you all meet someone who values you more than you do. " Sep 18,2019, tang posted the message, along with a screenshot of the video for Jay Chou's promise not to cry.

"after this winter, next spring will come, and it will be better. I'm waiting for spring, but if it's you, then spring won't be worth mentioning, " Tang added in the early hours of Dec. 13,2019.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In his circle of friends, he shares his thoughts about his feelings and his life.

In the chat, Tang Fan and Wang Sinan agreed: The speed of their success must exceed the speed of their parents aging. He thinks"successful"criterion is: take an examination of chief technician, monthly income exceeds ten thousand. To ease the burden on his family, he once told Wang Sinan that he wanted to work two jobs.

In mid-to-late January, a new outbreak of pneumonia, the country's medical staff into a high state of tension in the work. There was the first confirmed case in Fujian Province in Lianjiang County of Fuzhou City, and Wang Sinan soon entered the working state of fighting the epidemic. "On the second day of the Lunar New Year, he entered the quarantine area and was later assigned to the throat swab sampling group. " Until Wang Sinan entered the quarantine area, tang Fan, on the other hand, expressed envy. "He said he also wanted to get into the front line. "

In mid-february, two central quarantine observation points were set up in Licheng district of Quanzhou City, one of which was the Xinjia Hotel, where people from key areas of the epidemic in other provinces such as Hubei and Wenzhou were quarantined for observation. Tang fan was then sent to the hotel as a member of the medical team to take charge of the daily epidemic prevention work, every two days off duty one day, 24 hours during the duty need to stay at the isolation point, the isolation staff for daily temperature measurement and other work.

At 8 a.m. on March 7, as usual, Tang Fan and his mother headed to work. No one knows. Danger is creeping in.

At about 19:15 that day, the Xin Jia Hotel in Quanzhou collapsed and Tang Fan, who was on duty, was buried under the rubble. At about 20:00, Tang Shuangping learned of the hotel accident, immediately called his son's phone, but has not been answered. Arriving at the scene, in ruins, firefighters in orange and yellow overalls are scrambling to help.

"My son has turned off his phone now, and my cell phone has run out of power. I don't know what to do. " When a reporter at the scene lent Tang the charger, his hands trembled and he failed several times to insert the cord into the phone.

The next two days, in addition to waiting at the rescue site, Tang Shuangping also received treatment of the rescued hospital a home to ask, did not find his son.

On the afternoon of March 10, Tang Shuangping was notified to the funeral home to identify his son's body, confirmed that his son had been killed, Tang Shuangping collapsed.

"twenty-one years ago, you gave me hope for a life, and 21 years later, you pushed me into endless despair. " Tang wrote about his grief in a circle of friends.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In the face of his son's death, Tang Shuangping was filled with grief.

The accident has killed 28 people, including Tang. "after preliminary investigation, there are serious problems in the construction, renovation and approval of Xinjia Hotel, " Hong Ziqiang, executive vice mayor of the Quanzhou city government, said at a news conference on March 11, the reasons for the construction, renovation and operation of the building, including the selection of the isolation point, will be investigated and those responsible for violations of laws and regulations involved will not be tolerated.

Aunt Tang Fan introduced, because of excessive grief, Tang fan mother has been bedridden, Tang Shuangping also often silently wipe tears, "how good a child, too sorry. "
